  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>Fleshes out the definition for the special linear group over the Octonions which John Baez sketched out in his review paper on the Octonions. But Petyt arrives at a different result for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathrm {SL}_{3}(\mathbb {O})]]></fr:tex> than Sudbury.</html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
